CREATE TABLE Orders (
  order_id INT,
  product_name VARCHAR(255),
  order_date DATE,
  delivery_date DATE
)
CREATE TABLE Orders (order_id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_name VARCHAR(255), quantity INT, customer_name VARCHAR(255), delivery_date DATE)

CREATE TABLE Orders (
    order_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    unit_price DECIMAL(10,2),
    order_date DATE,
    delivery_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE Customers (
    customer_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    customer_name VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255),
    phone_number VARCHAR(20),
    address TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Products (
    product_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    product_name VARCHAR(255),
    description TEXT,
    category VARCHAR(50),
    price DECIMAL(10,2)
);
